PH4NTXM — LEGAL NOTICE

1. Purpose

PH4NTXM is distributed as an open-source operating system designed for lawful security research, privacy enhancement, and system auditing.
It provides a controlled environment for professionals, researchers, and operators to study, test, and improve information security systems.

