PH4NTXM must be used in accordance with applicable laws, regulations, and ethical standards.
Use of any included security, auditing, or penetration testing tools against systems without explicit, written authorization from their owners is strictly prohibited and may be unlawful.
Users are solely responsible for obtaining and retaining appropriate authorization prior to conducting any testing or analysis.

